---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Jai Long Co. Case Study | Dino Favara Jr."
  description="Built an entire content identity from scratch. 400 average views to 655,945 total views in 60 days."
>
  <Nav />

  <main>
    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-10">
      <a href="/work" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-primary/70 hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-200">
        &larr; All case studies
      </a>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-8 pb-12">
      <span class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-700 tracking-wide mb-6">
        Brand Build from Zero
      </span>
      <h1 class="font-display text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,3.2rem)] leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-dark mb-4">
        Jai Long Co.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg font-light text-dark/60 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
        Built an entire content identity from scratch. 400 average views to 655,945 total views in 60 days.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-6">
        {['Brand Identity', 'Content Architecture', 'Format Creation', 'TikTok Strategy', 'Podcast Clips'].map(tag => (
          <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-dark/10 bg-white/60 text-xs font-medium text-dark/55">{tag}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/70 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_1fr]">
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Avg Views Before</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-red-500">400</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">per video</span>
          </div>
          <div class="hidden md:flex items-center justify-center px-4"><span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&rarr;</span></div>
          <div class="flex md:hidden items-center justify-center py-2"><span class="text-2xl text-dark/20">&darr;</span></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 px-8 text-center bg-periwinkle/6">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/40 mb-3">Total Views After</span>
            <span class="font-display text-[2.8rem] leading-none text-primary">655.9K</span>
            <span class="mt-2 text-sm font-light text-dark/50">in 60 days</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-12">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        {[
          { value: '3,525', label: 'TikTok Followers', sub: '(from 216)' },
          { value: '106.6K', label: 'Top Video Views', sub: '' },
          { value: '29.6K', label: 'Total Likes', sub: '' },
          { value: '1,532%', label: 'Follower Growth', sub: '' },
        ].map(m => (
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-5 text-center">
            <span class="font-display text-2xl text-primary">{m.value}</span>
            <p class="mt-1 text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-dark/45">{m.label}</p>
            {m.sub && <p class="mt-0.5 text-[10px] text-dark/35">{m.sub}</p>}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
      <article class="prose-custom">
        <h3>The Situation</h3>
        <p>Jai Long is a business coach for creative professionals, specifically wedding photographers. He had a TikTok account with 216 followers, 830 likes, and content that was beautifully produced but had zero strategic architecture. His videos were averaging around 400 views. The production quality was there, but the content system wasn't.</p>

        <h3>The Approach</h3>
        <p>This was a ground-up build. I designed the entire content identity from scratch, centered on three pillars:</p>
        <p><strong>1. Positioning clarity:</strong> We tightened his bio and content thesis to "Business coach for creatives." Simple, searchable, and immediately clear to TikTok's algorithm.</p>
        <p><strong>2. Format library:</strong> I created multiple recurring formats including "30 Seconds with Jai" (quick-hit advice), podcast clip highlights, debate-style content like "Should You Work For Free?", and personal story hooks.</p>
        <p><strong>3. Podcast-to-short-form pipeline:</strong> Jai had a podcast with great material sitting unused. I built a system to identify the highest-value clips, edit them for short-form, and distribute them with platform-native packaging.</p>

        <h3>The Results</h3>
        <p>In 60 days, Jai generated 655,945 total views. He went from 216 to 3,525 followers, a 1,532% increase. His breakout video hit 106,600 views, with additional videos reaching 22.7K, 13.3K, and 11.4K views.</p>
        <p>More critically, Jai now had a system he could run independently. The format library, the podcast clip pipeline, and the content calendar were designed to be self-sustaining.</p>
      </article>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-dark/8">
        <span class="text-sm font-light text-dark/45">Timeline: 60 days</span>
        <div class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-full rounded-full bg-dark/6 overflow-hidden">
          <div class="h-full rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-periwinkle to-mint" style="width: 33%"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pb-20">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-dark/8 bg-white/60 p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div>
          <p class="font-display text-xl text-dark">Want results like this?</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-light text-dark/55 mt-1">Let's talk about building your content engine.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="mailto:dino@mercurysocialmedia.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 rounded-full bg-primary text-off-white font-medium text-sm hover:bg-primary/90 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/40 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 active:scale-95 whitespace-nowrap">
          Email me &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose-custom h3 { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--dark); margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .prose-custom h3:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose-custom p { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.65); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .prose-custom strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--dark); }
  .prose-custom blockquote { border-left: 3px solid var(--primary); padding: 1rem 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; background: rgba(107, 92, 231, 0.04); border-radius: 0 0.75rem 0.75rem 0; }
  .prose-custom blockquote p { font-family: 'Instrument Serif', serif; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .prose-custom blockquote cite { font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(26, 21, 35, 0.45); }
</style>
